in months over here.

00:07:39.902 --> 00:07:40.610
You keep talking.

00:07:40.610 --> 00:07:41.420
We'll get this thing rolling.

00:07:41.420 --> 00:07:41.680
JAMES SYHABOUT: OK.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:42.610
Cool.

00:07:42.610 --> 00:07:47.820
So I'm not sure if
this is Oscar Mayer.

00:07:47.820 --> 00:07:51.690
But it doesn't have to be.

00:07:51.690 --> 00:07:54.230
It's just a funny thing.

00:07:54.230 --> 00:07:57.260
SCOTT GIAMBASTIANI:
Get that one on high.

