00:11:37.650 --> 00:11:38.930
Some are sweeter.

00:11:38.930 --> 00:11:40.540
Same thing with fish sauce--

00:11:40.540 --> 00:11:46.520
in the book, there's a landscape
photo of all the bottled sauces

00:11:46.520 --> 00:11:49.720
and stuff you would use.

00:11:49.720 --> 00:11:53.922
So I did that just because,
sometimes, your mind spins

00:11:53.922 --> 00:11:55.630
when you go to an
Asian market, you know?

00:11:55.630 --> 00:11:58.610
You're staring at the soy
sauce shelf for, like, an hour.

00:11:58.610 --> 00:12:00.520
I'm like, which
one am I getting?

00:12:00.520 --> 00:12:03.985
So I made that picture,
so, pretty much, you

00:12:03.985 --> 00:12:11.056
