photo and just know the labels.

00:12:11.056 --> 00:12:14.960
This is makrut lime leaves
or kaffir lime leaves.

00:12:14.960 --> 00:12:17.680
A little bit of chiffonade then.

00:12:17.680 --> 00:12:20.680
We don't waste anything in our
household, even the little old

00:12:20.680 --> 00:12:26.120
end bits, unlike Commis,
where we waste everything.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:28.330
We like a perfect leaf.

00:12:28.330 --> 00:12:29.260
Use 10% of it.

00:12:29.260 --> 00:12:30.429
Throw away the rest.

