00:53:47.654 --> 00:53:48.570
JAMES SYHABOUT: Sorry.

00:53:48.570 --> 00:53:50.353
I didn't mean to make a mess.

00:53:50.353 --> 00:53:54.902
[LAUGHS] Cool.

00:53:54.902 --> 00:53:55.860
How's the food tasting?

00:53:55.860 --> 00:53:56.445
SCOTT GIAMBASTIANI:
It's delicious.

00:53:56.445 --> 00:53:58.770
JAMES SYHABOUT: Thank you to the
